task.summary: Changed security of the alert email gateway, as security by obscurity is no security. Especially when you publish it on GitHub :P
Raising baud rate to a maximum that ceramic resonator can reliably support. Decreasing timeout to 2 seconds.
Updated water meter Munin plugin to show Gallons per hour, instead of simple counter.
Added indoor "weather" graphs to Munin (with just water main probe for now)
Added 2 wireless probes to indoor weather graphs
Added a safeguard that would classify too high values as unknown.
Added motion sensor monitoring, and adjusted label for moved radio temperature sensor
Added soil moisture sensor to munin monitoring.
Fixed soil moisture polling: bug with too old data, all sensors' data got discarded if one was not received for a while.
Adding water leak monitor: looking at munin 5 minute averages over the past few hours and counting 0 readings.
Adjusting soil sensors Munin logic to show graph for at least one, if one has too old data.
Adjusting water leak sensor to take last 12 hours, instead of 6, as it is too low of a window for 5 minute resolution.
Adding new temp&humidity sensor to munin; adding dht module to reuse temperature parsing routines.
Increased water leak alert. Added one more humidity & temp sensor in the utility room.
Fixed labels on soil sensor data
